imdb.plot outline: William Brake was the best agent of the D.I.C.K (Deadly Investigator Consultant for Kicking- asses). On a mission to Mexico (French Emprire), under cover of SLUT (Supra Leadership of United Territories) and in collaboration with the DUMB (Destruction United for Mondial Be- happy), William Brake is ambushed by members of the OAS (Organization Terribly Secret). After horrible torture of William Brake, and the murder of his partner before his eyes, he is interned for several months. However, the Director made it back into the DICKdespite the negative opinion of his childhood friend, Raymond, and the College of Physicians Euthanasistes (Let never listen, yet "have you said "). William Brake therefore returns to service, still feverish and regularly disturbed by strange visions.
